        $materia->setConteudo('<p><span class="notranslate" style="color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 22.3999996185303px;"><b>A Axis of Awesome</b>&nbsp;é um australiano&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Musical_comedy&amp;usg=ALkJrhjWTTYOytklA5GMuhlrjnkvFP38jw" title="Comédia musical" class="mw-redirect" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">comédia musical</a>&nbsp;ato com membros&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jordan_Raskopoulos&amp;usg=ALkJrhiR_V7pYsh5Lts2q0wTPE18V30lJA" title="Jordan Raskopoulos" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Jordan Raskopoulos</a>&nbsp;, Lee Naimo e Benny Davis.</span><span style="color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 22.3999996185303px;">&nbsp;</span><span class="notranslate" style="color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 22.3999996185303px;">O trio cobrem uma ampla variedade de estilos de desempenho e realizar uma combinação de materiais e paródias pop originais.</span></p>
<h2 style="color: black; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(170, 170, 170); font-size: 1.5em;line-height: 1.3; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span class="notranslate"><span class="mw-headline" id="History">História</span>&nbsp;</span></h2>
<p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;"><span class="notranslate">A Axis of Awesome formada em 2006, seu nome sendo um jogo na frase "&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Axis_of_evil&amp;usg=ALkJrhgbY_mqIUB4sxj3JYgDpvrQjMf-WQ" title="Eixo do mal" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">eixo do mal</a>&nbsp;", usada por Estados Unidos&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/President_of_the_United_States&amp;usg=ALkJrhiF9FTOFp3ZeRg75VTit31Ey9VkLA" title="Presidente dos Estados Unidos" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Presidente</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_W._Bush&amp;usg=ALkJrhhBbfRJnS8Q8s5Xan3McpHflohNJg" title="George W. Bush" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">George W. Bush</a>&nbsp;.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notranslate">O trio foi fortemente envolvido no&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Improvisational_theatre&amp;usg=ALkJrhgC4rbVYZWoHEpOxs1y7_HZ0UnVuA" title="Teatro de improviso" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">improv</a>&nbsp;teatro na&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Sydney&amp;usg=ALkJrhgtvbAlbr5AL-vgiMfHRRjd-oGBIA" title="University of Sydney" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Universidade de Sydney</a>&nbsp;e decidiu tentar algo diferente.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notranslate">A banda tocou em alguns resistem noites de comédia de improvisação e eventos em Sydney e realizou um segmento quinzenalmente em&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FBi_Radio&amp;usg=ALkJrhhswyL3HibfPnJ6R5ppv7hyeL9UYw" title="FBi Radio" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">FBi Radio</a>&nbsp;, mas tem sua primeira grande chance quando eles lançaram uma série de paródias de rap satirizando a&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2007_Australian_Federal_Election&amp;usg=ALkJrhip5HgqbAK-AfTK5qfOZnfWq9VkJw" title="2007 Australian Eleição Federal" class="mw-redirect" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">2007 Australian Eleição Federal</a>&nbsp;.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;"><span class="notranslate">A banda ganhou ainda mais sucesso realizando no&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melbourne_International_Comedy_Festival&amp;usg=ALkJrhhqpoolozpZhJtmL4U0_9pXHznUSw" title="Melbourne International Comedy Festival" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Melbourne International Comedy Festival</a>&nbsp;e fazendo aparições na televisão e rádio.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notranslate">Sua Melbourne International Comedy Festival show de 2008, intitulado "A Axis of Awesome retorno espetacular", recebeu um&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moosehead_Award&amp;usg=ALkJrhhFcMho-hiptcLVg9SK_0Ey58FXbQ" title="Moosehead Award" class="mw-redirect" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Prêmio Moosehead</a>&nbsp;.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notranslate">Eles levaram o show para o&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edinburgh_Fringe&amp;usg=ALkJrhheG4RvCE3QOBJjIsb2B5PcWpo5xQ" title="Edinburgh Fringe" class="mw-redirect" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Fringe de Edimburgo</a>&nbsp;, em 2008, onde foi recebido com aclamação da crítica e público.&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Axis_of_Awesome&amp;usg=ALkJrhjfCFIW1APbxK32tWQPzuu3WhiILA#cite_note-1" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;"><sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.1999998092651px; unicode-bidi: embed;">[1]</sup></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Axis_of_Awesome&amp;usg=ALkJrhjfCFIW1APbxK32tWQPzuu3WhiILA#cite_note-2" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;"><sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.1999998092651px; unicode-bidi: embed;">[2]</sup></a></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;"><span class="notranslate">Depois do festival de Edimburgo, The Axis da canção de impressionante "&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/4_Chords&amp;usg=ALkJrhj4LNnXElYo2pnuaoOG5Lkyai8Qgg" title="4 Chords" class="mw-redirect" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">4 Chords</a>&nbsp;", um medley de 36 canções pop que todos contêm a mesma estrutura básica de acordes, recebeu airplay na&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BBC_Radio_1&amp;usg=ALkJrhjHQfsm4ATkXSHTWLaIbIyeQtUldA" title="BBC Radio 1" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">BBC Radio 1</a>&nbsp;.&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Axis_of_Awesome&amp;usg=ALkJrhjfCFIW1APbxK32tWQPzuu3WhiILA#cite_note-3" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;"><sup id="cite_ref-3" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.1999998092651px; unicode-bidi: embed;">[3]</sup></a>&nbsp;Esta airplay levou ouvintes para a internet e "4 Chords "se tornou viral, recebendo milhões de visitas em&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube&amp;usg=ALkJrhjCJis_NiWkBgulR0_oO00Cpt5g3w" title="Youtube" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">YouTube</a>&nbsp;.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notranslate">O sucesso no YouTube solicitado interesse crescente, tanto em casa como no exterior, ea Axis cantou a música em muitos programas de rádio e televisão, incluindo&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nova_96.9" title="Nova 96,9" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Nova 96,9</a>&nbsp;,&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Triple_M&amp;usg=ALkJrhgmWhC2Dw2wDMUl-jqhjXUlpQ9ieQ" title="Triple M" class="mw-redirect" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Triple M</a>&nbsp;,&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Footy_Show_(rugby_league)&amp;usg=ALkJrhiAeBtJrbZh8Jtyud3T2sIf52oLTw" title="The Footy Show (rugby league)" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;"><i>The Footy Show</i></a>&nbsp;,&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Good_News_Week&amp;usg=ALkJrhiydMchPpdpdMrrfioIALWimdXQwQ" title="Boa Semana Notícias" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;"><i>Good News Week</i></a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/9am_with_David_%2526_Kim&amp;usg=ALkJrhjHZjVO4r8pzBczJzRrDJ8B3EVWBA" title="09:00 com David &amp; Kim" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;"><i>09:00 com David &amp; Kim</i></a>&nbsp;.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;"><span class="notranslate">Em abril de 2009, a Axis of Awesome realizado no&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melbourne_International_Comedy_Festival&amp;usg=ALkJrhhqpoolozpZhJtmL4U0_9pXHznUSw" title="Melbourne International Comedy Festival" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Melbourne International Comedy Festival</a>&nbsp;com um novo show, The Axis of Awesome vs Bee.&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Axis_of_Awesome&amp;usg=ALkJrhjfCFIW1APbxK32tWQPzuu3WhiILA#cite_note-4" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;"><sup id="cite_ref-4" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.1999998092651px; unicode-bidi: embed;">[4]</sup></a>&nbsp;O show teceu canções da banda em uma narrativa envolvendo uma abelha gigante.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notranslate">A Axis of Awesome vs abelha também foi realizado no Sydney Festival de Comédia (anteriormente The Cracker Comedy Festival) em Maio de 2009.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;"><span class="notranslate">A Axis excursionou Queensland regional e Nova Gales do Sul, como parte do Festival roadshow Melbourne Comédia e se apresentou no&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adelaide_Cabaret_Festival&amp;usg=ALkJrhhIRNJRZvLVVSnqb4waVui7y1Mygg" title="Adelaide Cabaret Festival" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Adelaide Cabaret Festival</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Axis_of_Awesome&amp;usg=ALkJrhjfCFIW1APbxK32tWQPzuu3WhiILA#cite_note-5" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;"><sup id="cite_ref-5" class="reference" style="line-height: 1; font-size: 11.1999998092651px; unicode-bidi: embed;">[5]</sup></a>&nbsp;em maio e junho.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notranslate">Eles voltaram para a franja de Edimburgo em agosto com um novo show de sell-out "A Axis of Awesome: Infinito Rocha Explosão" e apareceu no&nbsp;<a href="https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&amp;hl=pt-BR&amp;prev=search&amp;rurl=translate.google.com.br&amp;sl=en&amp;u=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World%27s_Funniest_Island&amp;usg=ALkJrhgg7uCzNLMZH95ty7EAPds8QzGAjQ" title="Funniest Ilha do mundo" style="color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none;">Funniest Ilha do mundo</a>festival em Sydney em outubro.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;"><span class="notranslate">Em fevereiro de 2010, The Axis of Awesome lançou seu segundo álbum&nbsp;<i>Infinito Rocha Explosão!</i>&nbsp;Realizada e vendido para fora temporadas no The Adelaide Fringe Festival, The Melbourne International Comedy Festival, The Comedy Festival Sydney e The Flipside Festival Cingapura.</span>&nbsp;<span class="notranslate">Eles receberam A Time Out prêmio de melhor talento local no festival de comédia Sydney e gravou seu primeiro DVD,&nbsp;<i>O Axis of Awesome ao vivo</i>&nbsp;que foi lançado na Austrália em 6 de Outubro de 2010 pela Punchline and Beyond Entertainment.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: 22.3999996185303px; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;"><span class="notranslate">Eles voltaram para o Festival de Edimburgo novamente em 2014 com seu novo espetáculo "Viva La Vida Loca Las Vegas".</span></p>
